item.title: CVE-2017-13674|2024-08-05T19:05:19.125Z -- symantec%20corporation -- proxyclient
item.description: Symantec ProxyClient 3.4 for Windows is susceptible to a privilege escalation vulnerability. A malicious local Windows user can, under certain circumstances, exploit this vulnerability to escalate their privileges on the system and execute arbitrary code with LocalSystem privileges.
